  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is a large buffet of hot and cold items including fresh bread and pastries from the family bakery. Homemade jams, local cheeses, eggs and yoghurts and a selection of teas and coffees are included too.</p>
<p>In the evenings, you can look forward to a delicious four-course meal from the hotel's talented chefs</p>
<p>The hotel also has a café, sun terrace and hotel bar where they serve their own beer</p>]]></cateringDescription>
